gh we find that this specific\nempirical test of the HZ may be prohibitively challenging in the JWST era, the\nHBAR framework developed in this work may find a more immediate usage for the\nanalysis of gas giant spectra observed with JWST, Ariel, and other upcoming\nmissions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Feb 2022 19:00:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-02"}
