bserved line fluxes. This study highlights how\nmulti-molecular studies are essential for constraining the physical and\nchemical properties of the gas in populations of protoplanetary disks and that\nCO isotopologues alone are not sufficient for determining the mass of many\nobserved disks.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Feb 2022 19:01:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-30"}
