\nwearable-device-based measures of physical activity and body mass index among\nadults living in the United States.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Feb 2022 19:04:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 9 Nov 2022 06:35:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-10"}
