ants of their quasitopy classes.\nThen we prove that the quasitopies $\\mathcal{QT}_d(Y, \\mathbf c\\Theta)$ often\nstabilize, as $d \\to \\infty$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Feb 2022 03:15:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Apr 2022 01:27:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-04-19"}
