ur vortex shedding periods and retains\nonly a spatiotemporal invariance consisting in the evolution by half a period\n(two vortex-shedding cycles) followed by mirror reflection about a\nstreamwise-cross-stream plane. At slighlty higher values of $R\\geq4$, the flow\nhas become spatio-temporally chaotic, but the main features of mode C are still\nclearly distinguishable.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Feb 2022 14:42:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
